day 4 morinig concepts is 
system monitoring and resource utilization (free, df,du)

1)
monitor the sysem Memory 
free
free -t => shows the total memory
free -s 6 -> refresh every or shoes the output every 6 sec
free -h -> provides human readable output

2) 
checking disk space  usage for mounted devices
df command --> it is used to check the disk space in higher level eg: C drive, D drive so on

df -h
df -T = include type collumn
df -i -> include i node(file and directory)

3) disk space du
du  --> it is used to check the space in specific directory, or in a granual layer.
du -c -> shows total space
du -k shows in KB
du -h -> human readable

